data.description: Here's Gates at Kings Springs's latest gem! Convenient and just minutes away from Truist Park, The Battery, Silver Comet trail, restaurants, shopping, parks, walking trails & so much more! Luxurious 3 bedroom/3.5bathroom-2-Car garage chateau nestled in a cozy, gated townhome community. Chef's kitchen including 42" white cabinets, quartz countertops and an extra-large island with seating/breakfast bar & stainless-steel appliances, family room with 10ft. ceilings & the great room features a shiplap fireplace with cedar mantel, flanked by built-in floating bookcases. Private Patio off the main sitting room is perfect for entertaining. The entry level has a guest bedroom with a full bathroom, large foyer and custom drop zone with mudroom area. This smart home features a security system that makes monitoring and control features a breeze from your phone.    *HOME IS OCCUPIED, DO NOT SHOW WITHOUT CONFIRMED APPOINTMENT. Please be sure to use ShowingTime*    Seller is offering $5000 in seller's concession towards closing cost, rate buy-down etc.
